                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> Barsemis Abbei <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> alae firmae </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Kata&amp;lt;f=P&amp;gt;ractariae <lb n="2"/>ex numero <expan><ex>H</ex><abbr>os</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>ro&amp;lt;en&amp;gt;<surplus>ru</surplus>orum <expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>ister</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> |(miliariae) Hemes<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>n</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omo</ex></expan> Carris et <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elia</ex></expan> Iulia coniux <lb n="7"/>&amp;lt;ei=PL&amp;gt;us <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Aurelia Thicimim </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et Aurelia Salia &amp;lt;e=F&amp;gt;t <lb n="2"/>filias <note>sic</note> Barsimia Tit<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>ia</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>? nep</supplied><expan><abbr>ot</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> s<expan><ex>upra</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Abacus auf der Corona ist trapezförmig nach oben verlängert und zeigt an seiner Front eine Opferszene im Relief. Z. 1-2 befinden sich unterhalb des Reliefs, aber noch auf der Corona. (B): CIL III: Abweichungen in Lesung/Ergänzung.</p>
